ᱱᱚᱶᱟ ᱟᱹᱛᱩ ᱨᱮ [[ᱦᱳᱲᱳ]], [[ᱡᱚᱸᱰᱨᱟ]] ᱟᱨ ᱩᱛᱩ ᱟᱲᱟᱜ ᱡᱚ ᱮᱢᱟᱱ ᱠᱚ ᱪᱟᱥᱵᱟᱥ ᱠᱚ ᱠᱚᱨᱟᱣ ᱮᱫᱼᱟ ᱾<ref name="census2011.co.in">{{cite web | title=Chhotki Pona Village Population - Chitarpur - Ramgarh, Jharkhand | website=census2011.co.in | url=https://www.census2011.co.in/data/village/369164-chhotki-pona-jharkhand.html | access-date=2020-07-13}}</ref>

